configures reminder settings on user or guild, or provides the current configuration for the specified user or guild
```
!r config <option> <value> [--server]
!r config [@user|--server]
```
### Available options
- **timezone**
configs timezone for user or guild with format **hh:mm*
### Examples
provides your current configuration
```
!r config
```
provides current configuration for the user
```
!r config @some.guy
```
provides current configuration for the guild
```
!r config --server
```